entries.s_13: In the corner there, no, don't look, is a bounty hunter by the name of Boba Fett. He's part of the reason why Solo won't find any solace here.
entries.s_15: But he's a bounty hunter. Why doesn't he just pick Solo up?
entries.s_17: He doesn't know that Solo is here, just that he is coming.
entries.s_22: So, how do you like Tansarii station? Interesting, isn't it?
entries.s_23: Get yourself off this station before you get yourself killed.
entries.s_7: I'm a friend of Han Solo. I need to know what's going on.
entries.s_9: Ah yes, Solo. He should leave the station, soon. Not only is he unwelcome by some here, he's being hunted.
